{"tid":2222711,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Party Room羅生門","createTime":"2020-09-29T09:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T12:54:21.000Z","uid":30873,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f2205a4efc885224cf59899efa0defe3f83bbc96","tid":2222711,"uid":30873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:21:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200929/FWXBM2UYHRGMLKNVIIFIUQJPQA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200929%2FFWXBM2UYHRGMLKNVIIFIUQJPQA%2F&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=cc34ff41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200929%2FFWXBM2UYHRGMLKNVIIFIUQJPQA%2F&h=000be55e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200929/FWXBM2UYHRGMLKNVIIFIUQJPQA/</a><br />\n<br />\n【16:30】《蘋果》刊出報道後，事件演變成羅生門。<br />\n<br />\n自稱是該「派對房間」真正負責人的黃小姐致電記者，聲稱今次是遭人所害。她承認，公司的保安CCTV確曾錄下部份顧客在派對房間內的親熱片段，但公司從沒故意把影片外洩，只是她姓林的男朋友曾與好友分享過一些CCTV片段，原意只是想講出有客人在房內做了不當的行為。<br />\n<br />\n可是，她的男友後來與這名好友及另一男子因為「電動滑板車電池售賣」的問題鬧翻了，大意是對方質疑黃的男友所賣的價值1萬元滑板車電池不是正版貨，但黃的男友否認，雙方遂曾激烈爭執。其後，黃女懷疑有人怨狠之下，把之前手機收到CCTV片段又或是以其他不當途徑取得的公司CCTV親熱片段在網上公開，作為報復。<br />\n<br />\n黃女聲稱，她及男友已就此事報警，<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">她又堅稱在派對房間內不是隱藏的針孔鏡頭，只是明顯可見的普通CCTV鏡頭，公司亦有通告提醒顧客派對房間內會有CCTV錄影，故她否認是故意偷拍顧客。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"905762a08e794b612f3e1f8d5786e339aaf99079","tid":2222711,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:24:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52dc36399438a70a21f552822b04e2460ff999e7","tid":2222711,"uid":193421,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:28:29.000Z","msg":"大佬你允許第三方拎黎同人私下分享都錯撚哂喇吓嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" cla